OL,3,CKeir Starmer welcomes Zelenskyy and EU
OL,4,Cleaders to No 10 for Ukraine talks
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fwelcomed Emmanuel Macron, Friedrich
OL,8,FMerz and Volodymyr Zelenskyy to No 10
OL,9,Fto discuss support for Ukraine.
OL,11,FStarmer was photographed shaking hands
OL,12,Fwith each leader at Downing Street as
OL,13,Fthey arrived on Sunday evening, with
OL,14,FFrench, Ukrainian, British and German
OL,15,Fflags on display around No 10 and a
OL,16,Fred carpet rolled out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
