PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780876973
OL,3,CKeir Starmer welcomes Zelenskyy and EU
OL,4,Cleaders to No 10 for Ukraine talks
OL,6,F"The main focus is our defence in the
OL,7,Fwar, greater co-operation for the
OL,8,Fsecurity of all of Europe in the area
OL,9,Fof air defence, and our shared view of
OL,10,Fdiplomatic prospects ` Europe must be
OL,11,Fpart of the negotiations and must be
OL,12,Fstrong," the Ukrainian leader wrote.
OL,14,FZelenskyy added that he would also
OL,15,Fmeet the King on Monday and thanked
OL,16,Fthe UK and Ukraine's other allies, who
OL,17,Fhe said were helping "strengthen the
OL,18,Fprotection of life and increase
OL,19,Fpressure on Russia for its aggression".
OL,26,@{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
