FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780876973
OL,3,CKeir Starmer welcomes Zelenskyy and EU
OL,4,Cleaders to No 10 for Ukraine talks
OL,6,FThe three leaders meeting Zelenskyy
OL,7,Fare some of Kyiv's staunchest allies,
OL,8,Fwith the UK and France leading the
OL,9,F"coalition of the willing" initiative
OL,10,Fto provide security guarantees for
OL,11,FUkraine as part of a peace process.
OL,13,FThe meeting comes on the day a Russian
OL,14,Fdrone strike damaged a storage centre
OL,15,Ffor spent nuclear fuel in the Kyiv
OL,16,Fregion, nine miles from the Chernobyl
OL,17,Fnuclear power plant.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
