FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780876973
OL,3,CKeir Starmer welcomes Zelenskyy and EU
OL,4,Cleaders to No 10 for Ukraine talks
OL,6,FThe attack sparked a fire that was
OL,7,Fextinguished within an hour and
OL,8,Fradiation remains within safe levels,
OL,9,Fofficials said.
OL,11,FZelenskyy hit out at the "extremely
OL,12,Fvile" strike saying it was "an
OL,13,Fincrease in Russia's brazenness".
OL,15,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency
OL,16,Fchief Rafael Grossi said the incident
OL,17,Fwas "deeply concerning" due to the
OL,18,Flarge amounts of nuclear material held
OL,19,Fat the facility.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@EO]tD@\OUuD@`O]
